    <LocalizedText>
        <!-- ================================================================ -->
        <!-- Event Start (A) -->
        <!-- ================================================================ -->
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_STORYTITLE" Language="en_US">
            <Text>The Yona</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_COMPLETION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>These 'Ionians' or 'Yona' are a fascinating people. Their cities abound with graceful columns and eerily lifelike statuary. Their philosophers do not speak of Dharma. Their warriors carry polearms and shields round as the full moon.</Text>
        </Row>
        <!-- ================================ -->
        <!-- Option A -->
        <!-- ================================ -->
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_A_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>We could learn from their art and architecture.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_A_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Story continues.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_A_IMPERATIVE" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Complete 2 Matha Unique Quarters.</Text>
        </Row>
        <!-- ================================ -->
        <!-- Option B -->
        <!-- ================================ -->
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_B_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>We shall send men to trade and proselytize our ways.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_B_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Story continues.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_B_IMPERATIVE" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Start a trade route with Greece.</Text>
        </Row>
        <!-- ================================ -->
        <!-- Option C -->
        <!-- ================================ -->
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_C_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>We must remain vigilant of these foreigners.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_C_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>
        <!-- ================================================================ -->
        <!-- Option A (Art and Architecture) -->
        <!-- ================================================================ -->
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_A_STORYTITLE" Language="en_US">
            <Text>The Yona: Indo-Greek art</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_A_COMPLETION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Our craftsmen have grown quite adept at adapting the styles of the Yona to our own uses. Indo-Corinthian capitals adorn our viharas and stupas. Statues of gods, yakshas, and bodhisattvas are carved with elaborate drapery.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_AA_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Their work will grace our greatest monuments!</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_AA_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>+2 [icon:YIELD_HAPPINESS] Happiness from Wonders.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_AB_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Their work will help expound Dharma to the Mauryan people.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_AB_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>{1_reward} and {2_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>
        <!-- ================================================================ -->
        <!-- Option B (Trade and Philosophy) -->
        <!-- ================================================================ -->
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_B_STORYTITLE" Language="en_US">
            <Text>The Yona: Indo-Greek contacts</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_B_COMPLETION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Riches and ideas flow between the Yona and the Maurya. Some Grecians come to our realm to support our temples and monasteries. Abroad, a monk named Mahadharmaraksita has gained renown for his efforts converting the Ionians.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_BA_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Let us encourage these Grecian migrants to settle amongst us.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_BA_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_BB_NAME" Language="en_US">
            <Text>Let us invite Mahadharmaraksita to come speak of his efforts.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_EVENT_FXS_THE_YONA_BB_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US">
            <Text>{1_reward}.</Text>
        </Row>
	</LocalizedText>
